high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the bathtub, in the back corner of the bathroom.
Pick up the green sponge that is in the bathtub.
Turn to your right  and go to the sink that is just past the bathtub, on your left.
Place the sponge in the sink, turn the water on, rinse out the sponge, turn the water off, and remove the sponge from the sink.
Turn to your right and walk to the shower, turn right again and go to the sink across from you.
Place the sponge in the bottom, left drawer, underneath the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge in the bathroom drawer.
